{"id":"d6d1367e-e687-41c3-b645-6faa1d3fd427","title":"1540/08/07: To Giovan Simone","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"786500b0-4488-48dc-bfca-5437b96a8fff","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, August 7th, 1540.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"c408b918-a360-49f0-8158-81d89ead2d17","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":3,"value":"8532f2fa-b614-4eed-9eae-586327f6a15a","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"9d1d4bf0-f271-4666-85a1-a7dac3b7b061","type":"block/alignment/right","start":0,"end":27,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"396f8a7b-9a1c-459a-878a-2c90ffa8351f","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"ec82611d-e323-4614-95b5-ea673d7d357b","type":"codex/time-reference","start":11,"end":26,"value":"8d4660fa-7748-41e2-bb5f-fb5fe82d10fb","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"d5d6af0a-7b39-497b-a285-6a79096606b3","type":"style/superscript","start":19,"end":20,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[{"id":"9d1d4bf0-f271-4666-85a1-a7dac3b7b061","type":"block/alignment/right","value":null,"metadata":[]}]},{"id":"49e39448-9e54-4f24-bcb8-a9b163564183","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"2595bf5d-976c-4155-b446-c4c56797606c","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Giovan\u00A0Simone,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0This morning, the 7th of August, 1540, I paid six hundred and fifty crowns of gold in gold to Bartolomeo Angelini, and this sum will be\u00A0handed over to you in Florence by Bonifazio Fazi for\u00A0the purchase of the farm at Pazzolatica. Therefore,\u00A0as soon as you have explained this to Michele [Guicciardini], and Bonifazio tells you he is authorised to\u00A0pay out seven hundred ducats at seven lire the ducat\u00A0in exchange for a duly executed receipt, you will be\u00A0able to take possession of the farm without further delay. Thou or the priest [Fattucci] had best go to discuss it with Bonifazio, and he will tell you all there\u00A0is to know.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"555a6353-cfeb-4a2e-b418-e29da8600578","type":"codex/meta-relation-reference","start":0,"end":12,"value":"b48827df-bd11-4e78-a726-4e748a19f6be","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"7398dacc-dc49-4277-be69-94209dc9274a","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":12,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"f7bf7f47-ee1f-4060-b026-78fb9a227649","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":12,"value":"d8b71a68-0171-4aa5-a446-69fbdbd88655","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"842eacea-52e8-4b15-a543-8e9da467ca9c","type":"codex/time-reference","start":17,"end":28,"value":"cf290bde-1353-4495-af4e-75bc254dc240","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"65c8c4d4-4438-4ad8-ac6c-eeae780d3e62","type":"codex/time-reference","start":35,"end":53,"value":"4980ef8c-8f67-4a95-a545-17e776eac547","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"95d083ff-459e-4566-9192-ffdc963d5628","type":"style/superscript","start":36,"end":37,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"ff40feae-7ea1-47ef-8760-44d6a9a93325","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":56,"end":56,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"fc95d9fb-67e8-42ac-9a19-c9d3af076ed9","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":63,"end":106,"value":"db7703d6-9463-40ed-94e6-76796aca93fa","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"af50c44c-b618-462e-80ca-890cfdc40d36","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":111,"end":129,"value":"fb54dfcb-d041-4304-b48b-05957401bbf7","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"5461de0c-7df0-4cff-a95b-380233e0d94c","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":141,"end":143,"value":"db7703d6-9463-40ed-94e6-76796aca93fa","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"80761c27-b0ec-4462-9200-eeaf140e3562","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":168,"end":170,"value":"d8b71a68-0171-4aa5-a446-69fbdbd88655","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{